-Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |website=Arizona Superior Court in Pima County|title=Case L5373439|date=March 22, 1997|access-date=October 27, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Powers Hannley|first=Pamela|title='Sham' Marriage Allegations Arise Against Arizona Congressional Candidate Col. Martha McSally|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/pamela-powers-hannley/sham-marriage-allegations_b_2036319.html|accessdate=November 4, 2012|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=October 31, 2012}}</ref> McSally is a triathlete.<ref name=people/>\n\nIn April 2018, a Tucson man was sentenced to 15 months in prison for threatening to assault and kill McSally.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Prendergast|first1=Curt|title=Tucson man gets 15 months in prison for threatening U.S. Rep. Martha McSally|url=http://tucson.com/news/local/tucson-man-gets-months-in-prison-for-threatening-u-s/article_e51e85b9-fa60-53da-928e-f86f5c1656df.html|accessdate=April 19, 2018|publisher=Arizona Daily Star|date=April 18, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Biography|United States Air Force}}\n* [[Women in the United States House of Representatives]]\n* ''[[Final Report of the Task Force on Combating Terrorist and Foreign Fighter Travel]]''\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* Bergquist, Carl, \"1st Air Force female pilot in combat reflects on career\", ''Aerotech News and Review'', December 22, 2006\n* SeniorWomen.com articles by author David Westheimer (USAF Reserve Lt. Col.) \"Women in Blue\" at [http://www.seniorwomen.com/articles/david/articlesDavidAirForce.html],[http://www.seniorwomen.com/articles/david/articlesDavidAirForceII.html] & [http://www.seniorwomen.com/articles/david/articlesDavidMartha.html]\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Martha McSally}}\n* [https://mcsallyforsenate.com/ Martha McSally for Senate official website]\n* [http://www.mcsally.house.gov/ U.S. Representative Martha McSally], official U.S. House website\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Arizona/Go